title: Bodies in Motion 30 Year Anniversary Shows with Gilad [MP4]
description:
The 1300 series of shows are Gilad's 10 - 30th anniversary shows. They feature a mixture of new and long-time team members that join Gilad for comprehensive workouts. There are occasional flash-backs to show what the reunion members used to look like in the 1980's.
